3. Orchestrator Agent (@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent)
4. Ollama Chat Model (@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.lmChatOllama)
5. RAG Vector Store (@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.vectorStoreInMemory)
6. Ollama Embeddings (@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.embeddingsOllama)
7. Database Service Tool (n8n-nodes-base.httpRequestTool)
