9. PDF Report Service Tool (n8n-nodes-base.httpRequestTool)

Exempel p친 node-konfigurationer:

{
  "name": "Webhook Trigger",
  "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
  "parameters": {
    "httpMethod": "POST",
    "path": "orchestrator",
    "responseMode": "lastNode",
    "options": {}
  }
}

{
  "name": "Workflow Configuration",
  "type": "n8n-nodes-base.set",
  "parameters": {
    "assignments": {
      "assignments": [
        {
          "id": "id-1",
          "name": "databaseServiceUrl",
          "value": "<__PLACEHOLDER_VALUE__URL to your database service workflow webhook__>",
          "type": "string"
        },
        {
          "id": "id-2",
          "name": "sentimentServiceUrl",
          "value": "<__PLACEHOLDER_VALUE__URL to your sentiment analysis service workflow webhook__>",
          "type": "string"
        },
        {
          "id": "id-3",
          "name": "pdfServiceUrl",
          "value": "<__PLACEHOLDER_VALUE__URL to your PDF report service workflow webhook__>",
          "type": "string"
        }
      ]
    },
    "includeOtherFields": true,
    "options": {}
  }
}

{
  "name": "Orchestrator Agent",
  "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
  "parameters": {
    "promptType": "define",
    "text": "={{ $json.userRequest }}",
    "options": {
      "systemMessage": "You are an orchestrator agent that coordinates specialized n8n workflow services to fulfill user requests.\n\nYour role is to:\n1. Analyze the user request and determine which specialized services are needed\n2. Call the appropriate service tools in the correct sequence\n3. Coordinate data flow between services\n4. Use the RAG knowledge base when you need contextual information\n5. Return the final result to the user\n\nAvailable specialized services:\n- Database Service Tool: Retrieves and processes data from databases\n- Sentiment Analysis Service Tool: Analyzes sentiment from social media or text data\n- PDF Report Service Tool: Generates and formats PDF reports\n- RAG Vector Store: Provides contextual knowledge retrieval\n\nIMPORTANT:\n- Each tool calls a separate n8n workflow via webhook\n- Pass relevant data as JSON in the tool calls\n- Wait for responses before proceeding to dependent steps\n- Combine results intelligently to fulfill the user request"
    }
  }
}

